title: Vincent Labonté
text: Vincent Labonté (born April 8, 1987) is a <a href="Mauritian">Mauritian</a> <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player who currently plays for <a href="Curepipe%20Starlight%20SC">Curepipe Starlight SC</a> in the <a href="Mauritian%20League">Mauritian Premier League</a> and for the <a href="Mauritius%20national%20football%20team">Mauritius national football team</a> as a <a href="Defender%20%28football%29">defender</a>.
